{"tid":691541,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"國際廢老： 紐約地鐵爭位坐 黑人婦護女辱罵亞裔婦","createTime":"2018-06-05T23:53:47.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-06T03:05:04.000Z","uid":157898,"like":44,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"c1fca6933916d07a300b151dfb3f6755e67c1c41","tid":691541,"uid":157898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-05T23:53:47.000Z","msg":"美國紐約一名亞裔婦日前在乘搭地鐵期間，要求一名小孩讓座而令其黑人母親不滿，黑人婦先是大聲以粗言辱罵亞裔婦，繼而動粗把亞裔婦推落地。亞裔婦全程要求黑人婦冷靜和注意言詞，惟對方情緒激動，更指亞裔婦不屬於美國。&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n網民上周三（5月30日）把上述片段上載到互聯網，可見黑人婦不滿亞裔婦奪去其女兒的座位，於是開始謾罵對方，警告不要玩弄其女兒，更直指亞裔婦是華人，會推開其女兒是因為她們是西班牙裔。黑人婦越來越激動，更把亞裔婦推離座位跌倒地上。&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n在場乘客扶起亞裔婦後，亞裔婦威脅要報警處理，黑人婦無視警告，斥罵：「這（美國）不是你的國家。」亞裔婦其後離開車廂，黑人婦的女兒亦重奪座位，但黑人婦仍繼續大聲宣洩不滿。該影片引起網民熱烈討論，有人認為黑人婦不應散播種族歧視言論；有網民則認為黑人婦只是在盡母親的責任保護女兒，相反亞裔婦不應推開別人的孩子。&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n力架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n廢老<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20180605/mobile/bknint-20180605190036319-0605_17011_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fint%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180605%2Fmobile%2Fbknint-20180605190036319-0605_17011_001.html&d=CnfZj3ErIPuV8b4ntSdHa%2F9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=9612adb3\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20180605/mobile/bknint-20180605190036319-0605_17011_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"56cc09b77ff499ce3c83c974e5d02b1e3d4dd491","tid":691541,"uid":51436,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-05T23:55:58.000Z","msg":"抵撚死"},{"pid":"f8af66686acbbdc2e45d9ca8e87a9c0815a0ead5","tid":691541,"uid":8048,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-05T23:57:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/03/092709_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F03%2F092709_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=e733597d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a9594f1b3220c69d1bc87c2ab913d06d97bc5c5f","tid":691541,"uid":105678,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T00:01:28.000Z","msg":"支那狗抵打<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c93a46db1a93b6b540b3ab65a36502b8a09e951a","tid":691541,"uid":42188,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T00:08:24.000Z","msg":"又贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ae7be510a4e74ab9e62e00c8c06c207672d888a","tid":691541,"uid":126977,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T00:18:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2291dcf9f37bc78bafd78b36447e7e21ceb1e6ed","tid":691541,"uid":17866,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T00:19:43.000Z","msg":"話人唔屬於美國<br />\n佢自己咪又係西裔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d58df711bc2fc42456522f6c8010456e6803ad9","tid":691541,"uid":53672,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T00:23:02.000Z","msg":"條片影到隔離個華人撓埋手扮聽唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 隻力架屌埋你都當無事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29fd7911127ad0a324ea6d5d429d9206b44c5bfa","tid":691541,"uid":13257,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T00:24:27.000Z","msg":"無睇片唔清楚，文字唔係話個亞裔女人要求黑人婦人個女讓座ja咩，做咩變咗玩弄同推開佢女兒。"},{"pid":"60f4e90c4197ece05734a4cbc67578fa3a57d7fe","tid":691541,"uid":34080,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T00:26:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ae5b9d54dc0f76a6e72bdee89a939f4e2b64356b","tid":691541,"uid":171786,"like":1,"dislike":0,"sco